Name: Artificial Wallpaper
About the game: When was the last time you changed your wallpaper? Why not change it everyday? Why not use AI do create a unique wallpaper for you? Artificial Wallpaper is an app created to show you a brand new wallpaper everyday. All you need to do is download it, run, click 'Update Wallpaper' and it's done. If you check the 'Start with Windows' option, then you need to do nothing else. Every day, when you turn your computer on, it will automatically change your wallpaper. If everyday it's too much for you, don't worry. You can take your time your time to enjoy this art. You can also choose to change every week, month or manually, when you feel like to. Just a small warning: due some limitations, we can not save your original wallpaper. So, please backup it first if you want to use it again (we hope you don't).
